would limit the amounts of greenhouse gases being released into the
atmosphere. If ratified, the Kyoto Protocol will require industrial
nations to dramatically reduce emissions of those gases by 2012.
Here, a look at how shifts in the weather and potential regulatory
changes will impact businesses. 1,400 words. By Kimberly O'Neill
