to leave the teaching profession.
</P>
<P>
   Next week I will discuss ways that we can all assist teachers in
their extremely important work.
</P>
<P>
   Dr. Hap LeCrone is a clinical psychologist. If you have
questions or topics you would like Dr. LeCrone to discuss, write
him at 4555 Lake Shore Drive, Waco, Texas 76710 or e-mail him at
hlecrone(at)aol.com.
</P>
