   TECH-MATCHMAKER (Boston) _ Joyce Plotkin, a soccer mom who was
reared in Wheeling, W.Va., is the great connection-maker in the
Massachusetts software industry. She lobbies government, raises
money, links up entrepreneurs with venture capitalists, and
introduces movers to shakers. And she does it all behind the
scenes. By Ross Kerber. (2 takes) PHOTO
