the NFC. (Atlanta Journal-Constitution).
</P>
<P>
   PAGE THREE
</P>
<P>
   NFL-AFC-CAPSULES _ A team-by-team look at strengths, weaknesses
and personnel changes. (Atlanta Journal-Constitution).
</P>
<P>
   NFL-AFC-PREVIEW _ Highlights, observations and predictions for
the AFC. (Atlanta Journal-Constitution).
</P>
