   There's a Giant Corn Maze with three miles of twisting walking
paths awaiting in Shelburne, Vt., by the home of the Vermont Teddy
Bear Co. (which is open for tours). There are lots of dead ends
with surprises, too. The maze is open daily through Labor Day and
weekends through October. For information, call 802-985-3001 or
visit www.VermontTeddyBear.com.
</P>
