   GORE _ M ILWAUKEE, Wis. _ Vice President Al Gore, rebutting
Republican charges that the U.S. military has grown weaker under
the Clinton administration, told the Veterans of Foreign Wars on
Tuesday that America's fighting forces are ``the strongest and the
