the almost-untouchable leader of semiconductors for the PC
business. But as PCs become passe and the Internet rules, Intel is
refocus itself on providing chips for everything Internet-related,
be they wireless Web phones or high-powered Internet servers. No
where is Intel's Internet emphasis more present than at its annual
developer's conference, which begins Tuesday in San Jose, where the
theme is ``Powering the Net.'' (Keefe, Austin American-Statesman).
