SAN FRANCISCO _  &UR; SECRET-SALAD &LR;  _ Few appetizers are as refreshing
and delicious as the melon salad at Ponzu. It's a marvelous
concoction created by John Beardsley. Chunks of watermelon,
honeydew and cantaloupe are bathed in lemongrass dressing made with
lemon and lime juice, ginger and a secret ingredient: Thai fish
sauce.
