<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-FALLEN-IDOLS-NNS </SLUG>
  
 NFL's Felonious Off-Season Renews Debate over Role Modeling for
Kids  
 ATTENTION EDITORS: This article from NEWHOUSE NEWS SERVICE for
TUESDAY, Aug. 22, is available as a ``separate-buy.'' For
information about purchasing the article, contact DEBRA WEYDERT of
The New York Times Syndicate at 1-212-499-3401; fax, 732-390-4697;
e-mail: weyded(at)nytimes.com.) 
 ATTENTION EDITORS: With seven photos, of Mark Chmura (NNS1), Rae
Carruth (NNS2), Paul Krumberger (NNS3 and NNS4), Brett Favre
(NNS5), Antonio Freeman (NNS6) and Darrell Green (NNS7). 
 By MARK O'KEEFE  
 c.2000 Newhouse News Service  
<TEXT>
