attention with a firm, ``Stay with me now.''
</P>
<P>
   Before he retires, Green, 40, said he wants to set aside $10
million for the foundation.
</P>
<P>
   ``Make sure you take care of things they can't take away from
you,'' Green told the children. ``In sports, you can break a leg.
But no one can take your honesty away from you. No one can take
your integrity away from you.''
</P>
<P>
   Walking to the locker room, Green said it is foolish to see Nike
spend millions of dollars on athlete endorsements to persuade
