<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-08-22 17:04 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A9154 &Cx1f; taf-z
u f BC-FED-RATES-440&AMP;ADD-NYT     08-22 0689
