   &UR; COMMENTARY (k) &LR;
</P>
<P>
   OLIPHANT-COLUMN (Los Angeles) _ For Al Gore, so far, so good. By
Thomas Oliphant.
</P>
<P>
   &UR; HEALTH/SCIENCE (a) &LR;
</P>
<P>
   SCI-PERIOD (Undated) _ A new movement questioning the necessity
of women's periods is building, this time led by researchers who
say menstruation is neither necessary nor even healthy. By Megan
Scott 1900 words.
