</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    1ST UPDATE
 &HT;    EDs: Adds: FIRESTONE, FIRESTONE-SIDE, CANE-MAIN, GORE-FLORIDA,
DIGITAL-STATION, KOOP
 &HT;    
 &HT;    CoxNet Cox News Service budget
 &HT;    FOR WEDNESDAY, Aug. 23, 2000
 &HT;    c. 2000 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
