<SLUG> BC-PHOTO-UPDATE-NYT </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
 
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
   ATTENTION EDITORS:
</P>
<P>
   The following photos have been sent as part of tonight's New
York Times Photo Package, moving Tuesday, 08/22/00.
